      "id": "mem_094",
      "sourceId": "qmd_31564",
      "source": "qmd",
      "text": "[Vault/Research] Research: Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week: # Research: Division 1 men's lacrosse games this week  ## Summary Based on the provided research data, the NCAA Division I Men's Lacrosse Championship semifinals and final are scheduled for Memorial Day weekend, specifically May 23-25, 2026, at Scott Stadium in Charlottesville, VA [1]. While some regular season games from March 2026 are listed as airing on ESPN+, the immediate \"this week\" schedule for current live games is not",
      "category": "general",
      "type": "fact",
