      "sourceId": "qmd_47113",
      "source": "qmd",
      "text": "House hunting requirements for a 65-year-old woman:\n- Budget for house: $400,000 (after taxes and retirement savings)\n- Location preference: Suburbs immediately outside Philadelphia, PA (Broomall, Upper Darby, Havertown are top choices)\n- House size: 900-2000 sq ft\n- Yard: Small, ideally fenced, for a dog\n- Key concern: Low taxes (must be below $8000 per year)",
